27:04.482 --> 27:11.850
We ask you to open our eyes and our ears, all of our senses to the miracles that are taking place all around us.

27:13.172 --> 27:16.495
I believe, Lord, help my unbelief.

27:16.796 --> 27:28.709
Dear God, we just ask that we can grow deeper spiritually because of your presence and the fact that we recognize your presence all around us.

27:29.990 --> 27:31.892
It's in Jesus' name that we pray.

27:32.173 --> 27:33.394
And all of God's people said,

